Windlord/Kup/DeathStar::

Windlord looked to Kup and said "Our plans has to change... a 
little..."And looking to Sure Strike and DeathStar said"After we 
find out what it's goin on we should go to help to buildt the Anti-
unicron gun... Let's go!!!"


Windlord and DeathStar Moved towards the exit, and Kup lookin to 
Kitkat and BlackFang said "BlackFang, can you show Kitkat where's 
the mess hall, after all if she decides left the base show her 
where's the exit... If she decides remains, tell report it to me or 
with ROdimus.."and looking to the little Cam said "Do you like still 
help me with some stuff that I need do???"

--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Jerame Johnson <jeramej@y...> wrote:
> 
> SureStrike:
> 
> Runs to the CR in hopes of finding someone to help. Upon seeing 
the Group in there He Yells to Winlord, "Winlord, Dragos and Argos 
are late in thier Check in, They are two days late. I tried the 
Communicators I created. They work Fine but the only problem is that 
they Cannot be tracked Outside of a 4 Kilometer range. 
Communications is still fine though. They told me that they were 
going to investigate a Disturbance that they Felt in a coastal Area. 
And nothing came back. Well I mean they Never Came back. I have to 
Go out after them RockTower is going with me, Same with Cheetar and 
I hope Cooley will go with," Looking towards Cooley.
> 
> Cooley:
> 
> Looking towards KitKat the towards Surestrike, "Man if Dragos goes 
down then that is is for my mission. All of ours that is. and Might 
be the end of the matrix. Lemme fix myself for a quick second And I 
will meet you at the Entrance in a couple Microns."
> 
>  
> 
> SureStrike: 
> 
> "Yeah, No problem." Surestrike heads out to the entrance.
